#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.18:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Vijjāsutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.430"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.18:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.2"
msgid "“‘vijjā, vijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.3"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, bhante, vijjā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.4"
msgid "kittāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ kho, bhikkhu, dukkhe ñāṇaṃ, dukkhasamudaye ñāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhe ñāṇaṃ, "
"dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ñāṇaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, vijjā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.18:1.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca vijjāgato hotīti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.18:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhu, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.18:2.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
